reviewText: Best pop techno band out there. This is a compilation of their videos. If you are a fan don't miss out.... It really is Japanese funk from the future!!!!

If you are a Perfume fan two of the items that you need to have in your collection is the Clips DVD's and Game CD. Their music is techno, good beat and a nice blend between the 3 singers.  Ordered it through K-I-M-JAPAN who wrapped it safely and shipped quickly. 100% happy with purchase.
